{"tid":567495,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[導演介紹] 惡夢製造者 David Lynch","createTime":"2018-02-21T02:12:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T07:03:19.000Z","uid":78390,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"00e7bc73bd3e95bd48f95a21cb4beb5ca93cbddd","tid":567495,"uid":78390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T02:12:50.000Z","msg":"David Lynch 可算係電影界最有影響力嘅人<br />\n他對藝術嘅熱情<br />\n創作不一樣嘅電影 追求唔再係講故事 而是一個體驗角色心理 帶俾觀眾一個經歷<br />\n雖然話過從此引退電影 不過佢留下嘅足跡都開括電影新境界<br />\nReady to get your mind fucked by David Lynch<br />\n<br />\nEraserhead<br />\nStanley Kubrick都話正 咁一定好睇<br />\n呢部電影其實好難解釋 其因David Lynch以夢的感覺去拍部電影 加上David Lynch唔會解釋自己故事 永遠留俾觀眾自己摸索<br />\n當中嘅恐怖 同角色不正常行為 不安畫面 都令人情緒不安<br />\n不過體驗一個惡夢都不錯選擇<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/100749_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F100749_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4494beda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/100756_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F100756_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3d205f9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMulholland Dr.<br />\n簡直神一般的作品<br />\n帶人入一個顛倒世界<br />\n電影業嘅黑暗面 追求名利而喪失自己<br />\n算David Lynch 高峰之作<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/100806_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F100806_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2e6ab9b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/100819_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F100819_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=57de58f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBlue Velvet<br />\n恐怖 迷離 仲記得睇個人好繃緊<br />\n一個好奇少年睇到社會黑暗一面<br />\n希望拯救一個受盡拆磨嘅女人<br />\n呢部電影令到David Lynch 得到Twin Peaks靈感 加上係David Lynch最危險電影<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/100837_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F100837_234c50d755a7bdf4dd5b45bf9ebe228a.jpeg&h=63579a79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/100848_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F100848_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f41e0c5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDune<br />\nDavid Lynch 自己都認為呢部係事業最失敗嘅作品<br />\n事實上就真係無David Lynch一貫作風 但又未至於咁差<br />\n配樂同特技(以當年標準)都算唔錯<br />\n鐘意科幻電影呢部都值得一看<br />\n加上Denis Villeneuve (Arrival 同Blade Runner 2049 導演)就快重拍呢本經典故事 當睇預告<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/100859_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F100859_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=beab418f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/100906_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F100906_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=69794f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe Straight Story<br />\nDavid Lynch 雖然强項主攻 experienmental movie <br />\n佢都拍過下温情電影<br />\n呢個簡單故事講述一個老人家探回佢快離世嘅兄弟<br />\n整部充滿人生哲理 而撲素的心去理解人性<br />\n充滿遺憾 也充滿感情 <br />\n都值得一看<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/100915_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F100915_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=2b097c05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nINLAND EMPIRE<br />\n呢套認真唔知拍乜 <br />\n不過係David Lynch最後一部電影 加上係全digital拍攝 特別不過唔知拍乜<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/100933_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F100933_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=afe91a9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe Elephant Man<br />\n少年得志 令佢進軍Hollywood<br />\n都不失自己style<br />\n也是對他地位的肯定<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/100944_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F100944_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8b527131&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTwin Peaks <br />\n佢係電視界都具影響力<br />\n到現在人都認為今天電視黃金時代都係因為Twin Peaks<br />\n改變整個電視創作方式<br />\n隔咗25年 都仲有fans 去支持拍續集<br />\n<br />\nTwin Peaks: Fire Walk with Me<br />\n大部分David Lynch電影影評都比較極端<br />\n呢部我認為最令人低估<br />\n當中David Lynch所實驗嘅橋段<br />\n加上Sheryl Lee完美演出<br />\n拍出一個人嘅內心世界與思想 所受過嘅痛苦同自我疑惑 都俾David Lynch 以鏡頭捕捉<br />\n有人可能因為冇睇過Twin Peaks會覺得悶<br />\n但呢部電影會令觀眾完全代入Laura 被殺前幾日嘅經歷<br />\n對Twin Peaks 係個完美Prequel<br />\n亦都係一部心路歷程故事完美演繹 <br />\n睇完會繞梁三日<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/100959_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F100959_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f9b8b774&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/101006_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F101006_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=514e3ccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLost Highway 同 Wild at Heart都係佢嘅作品<br />\n<br />\n想多了解David Lynch<br />\n可以睇佢本書 To Catch a Bigger Fish<br />\n<br />\n呢套紀錄片 David Lynch: The Art Life<br />\n睇佢做煙產<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/21/101216_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F101216_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=7dcb0c4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBroadway Cinematheque 都有出過關於佢嘅書 都篇幅咗唔少關於David Lynch 嘅故事同人們對佢嘅電影解讀"},{"pid":"eb94ca4ceab3dea8378e7253ef7023c13c4ba201","tid":567495,"uid":131259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T02:57:08.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"ba674fc703c6dd33fc4f6c6d111bc21eaea469f0","tid":567495,"uid":8199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T04:55:48.000Z","msg":"之前睇 mullholand dr. 睇到一頭霧水<br />\n要上網睇解說 再loop 套戲先叫做睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"130ac9f9a4df2e2c3dce3344ac639dc6a7da234a","tid":567495,"uid":27616,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T06:07:53.000Z","msg":"Mulholland Dr.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe797341850cc03af366e79d0cffe756257fb06","tid":567495,"uid":5595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T06:14:23.000Z","msg":"我淨係覺得佢個髮型好型"},{"pid":"825a230a15b9c193213f1466e0a3f9531459da7a","tid":567495,"uid":39576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T02:18:41.000Z","msg":"之前百老匯回顧番佢部分電影，睇左好多，真係好特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb89d78bc7904097d4986725ed326a586ef08b46","tid":567495,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T02:21:41.000Z","msg":"睇完覺得好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8200e9e9527255521a9d6e0228dbb29ede8b2f0","tid":567495,"uid":78390,"like":0,"dislike"